<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=EDGE">
    <meta name="renderer" content="webkit" />
    <meta http-equiv="pragma" content="no-cache" />
    <meta http-equiv="cache-control" content="no-cache" />
    <meta http-equiv="expires" content="-1" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>燃气认证门户系统</title>

    <link href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <link href="/css/animate.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/style.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/jquery/jquery-2.1.1.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body class="gray-bg">
    <div class="loginColumns animated fadeInDown">
        <div class="row" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h1 class="center-block" style="width:450px;">燃气认证门户系统</h1>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="login" class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <!-- <img class="center-block" style="width: 210px;" alt="image"  src="/img/cuit-logo.png"> -->
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="ibox-content">
                    <form class="m-t" role="form" method="POST" action="<%= originalUrl %>">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="text" id="username" name="username" class="form-control" placeholder="用户名" required="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="password" name="password" id="password" class="form-control" placeholder="密码" required="">
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" id="login-btn" class="btn btn-primary block full-width m-b">登陆</button>
                    </form>
                    <p class="m-t" id="errorDiv">
                        <% if (error) { %>
                            <p class='text-danger' id="errorP"><%= error ? error.message : '' %></p>
                        <% } %>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="chrome" class="row" style="display: none;">
            <div class="col-md-4"></div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h2>抱歉，您的浏览器版本过低，请选择使用IE9或者以上版本浏览器，或者Chrome和Firefox浏览器。</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4"></div>
        </div>
        <div id="chromeDownload" class="row" style="display: none;">
            <div class="col-md-4"></div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <p style="color:#FF5511;"><strong>快捷下载Chrome浏览器：</strong></p>
                <p>
                    <a href="http://210.41.229.137:9090/ChromeStandalone_52.0.2743.116_Setup.exe" target="_blank">
                        <img src="/img/chrome.jpeg" />
                    </a>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4"></div>
        </div>
        <hr/>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
         </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 text-right">
               <small>Copyright © CUIT © 2016</small>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
